Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:11.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译：最爱炮姐 小约 饭团粽子   后期：sslish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 都那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事还不能让我泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为了振作精神 一定要好好疯一把
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ABC席从南门入\NDES席从北门入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻妞 为什么不用羽衣隐身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A8区52号…52…52…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 这个座位是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂 桂木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天保佑不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 票是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那么好的席位居然重复预定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的 别傻站着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同学 这个座位让给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找有没有空着的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有空位的 一人坐一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行啦 老师怎么可以和学生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被别人看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 职业摔跤NOAH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉年华淘汰赛 最终决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这个席位是很棒啦…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选手入场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝方 秋川纯 三和光张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红方 石井角 杰布基·贾尼杰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋川是这团队的年轻王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的三和 那个人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会使出和巨汉鹤马一样的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完之后也会大叫「喔~」的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就是这样 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是那杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里 上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有个好位置感受到的气魄都不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后排的位置可感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠的这么近还是不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师和学生这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业摔跤这么有激情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤手之间用尽浑身解数碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他们的一举手一投足观众则会用掌声回应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后为之颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤能够这么有激情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为大家的步调都一致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤不仅仅是局限在擂台上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助着选手们的工作人员们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和观众们一起创造出了这场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你为什么就是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明为了你考虑了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就是不回应我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你我连游戏机都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很贵的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人的话是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是大家一起努力的话是办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个 篮球部毁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经休部的篮球部 队长还是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是你那一代被毁了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你毁了篮球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我现在觉得相同的事情会再度发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还会有人被你的理想所击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯 你做的太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再陪你疯下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都说了想要变得更强的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都要离去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了篮球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家 拼命的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 真的是为了大家着想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这种人又懂些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不理解我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能…看到结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「长濑 大家的烦恼咨询」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 如果是这个档次的话挺便宜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 一点都不便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说昨天  长濑老师给我打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这不正是你的目的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有点缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有些微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还发生过那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开班会之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有个建议要对大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}第24回舞岛马拉松大会\N招募参加者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的舞岛马拉松 大家一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要大家都去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经替大家提交申请了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦~哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就在马拉松中合而为一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通点就行了 普通点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是在演电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么还来找我商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还那样开心的和我说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会被说成像反派一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要被骂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这老师挺危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在成为真正的教师之前能看清现实对她来说也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 长濑也居然会搭理你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对你们这些满身是BUG的人做什么都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜宅男 你刚才都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮得到你在这说大话吗 不过是游戏狂热者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 眼镜宅男呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 到哪里都无所谓了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}41 42 43 44 45
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这课怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是为了大家才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要是大家能同心协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是只有不愉快的回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是令人讨厌的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底你才是我这次失败的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次本来一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经成为大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也学习了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为理想中的老师的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和以前一样什么都没改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要 不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不管是以前还是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是将自己的理想强加于别人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我该怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了努力什么都不会 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家越是离我远去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是想要帮助大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将理想更加强硬地塞给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要理会别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要做你内心认为正确的事就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不会跟着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在面对理想时 大家都会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不行的 不可能做到的」这样想着而逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你也必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管受到多大的伤 多么孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也必须展现出你的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像巨汉鹤马一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…老师 回教室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们不对 我们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我写好了如何到达结局的顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要按照我写着的那样来办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 长濑也居然会搭理你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对你们这些满身是BUG的人做什么都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑出去之后 我会对班上的人恶言相向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他们对长濑的不满重置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 在我出去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}42 43 44 45
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数到500之后 将班上的人引到体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑老师 完全没有回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么让人失落的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,499 500
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去迎接长濑老师回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 大家说的太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 同类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 我知道长濑老师会在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得稍微有点强硬的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家都来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现实 只有理想是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的结局也是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会成为一个好老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长濑老师的教育实习 也到今天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么神大人他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那天以后就再也没来过学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受您照顾了 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 有什么烦恼的话就来和我倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会听你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为再也见不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你是个孤独而且冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要 再回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会成为更棒的老师然后回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看到我不像老师的一面 这次是最后一次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来那个游魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:20.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG 11.0 将太阳永存于心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:35.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG 12.0 夏日大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作好游戏的条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像天使一样大胆地将故事展开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像恶魔一样纤细地把握住平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人类的灵魂注入角色中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的制作出烂游戏的理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 有各种各样的原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔是很纤细的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:05.52,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)}{\pos(596,352)}雪酷字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.20,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让机会溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.45,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.45,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么要剥夺我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.09,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.09,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与感性不同 理性更让我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:52.92,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:52.92,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必须跨越这挫败感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.42,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.42,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力将不会是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:59.49,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:59.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无尽的欲望 在心中不断反复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.80,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夹在理想与现实间的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.33,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.33,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一种可以改变世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.20,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.20,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走调又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.28,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.28,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手绘不佳也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:17.04,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:17.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只会为了追寻那唯一的信念而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.03,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.03,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一个只有神知道的崭新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.23,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我将永远伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你内心受到的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.13,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.13,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的骑士 做你的明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.57,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们会无比闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.12,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.23,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼泪 我们将不再惧怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.76,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.76,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所谓的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.83,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.22,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.83,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.22,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这不是现实中的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我会为你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.05,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.05,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生将会发生什么 我都将翻过此页跨上成人的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.76,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,441)\fs22}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.76,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,38)\fs22}记住 没人可以批判我
